ine":21,"column":0,"depth":2},"apa-yang-dicari-bmad-market-research":{"type":"header","text":"Apa yang dicari BMAD market research?","value":"apa-yang-dicari-bmad-market-research","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"kenapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Kenapa ini penting?","value":"kenapa-ini-penting","line":38,"column":0,"depth":2},"output-yang-berguna":{"type":"header","text":"Output yang berguna","value":"output-yang-berguna","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":55,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bmad-market-research-menangkap-realitas-eksternal-sebelum-planning\">BMAD market research menangkap realitas eksternal sebelum planning<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bmad-market-research-menangkap-realitas-eksternal-sebelum-planning\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Apa tujuan BMAD market research?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana ia berbeda dari sekadar \"cek kompetitor\"?</li>\n<li>Apa output yang membuat planning lebih tajam?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"klaim-utama\">Klaim utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaim-utama\"></a></h2>\n<p>BMAD market research bukan sekadar daftar pemain. Itu adalah upaya untuk memastikan bahwa ide produk tidak berjalan sebagai solusi untuk masalah yang hanya ada dalam kepala tim.</p>\n<p>BMAD menempatkan market research di phase awal agar produk yang akan direncanakan punya dasar realitas eksternal: kebutuhan nyata, ruang kompetisi, dan ruang diferensiasi.</p>\n<h2 id=\"apa-yang-dicari-bmad-market-research\">Apa yang dicari BMAD market research?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#apa-yang-dicari-bmad-market-research\"></a></h2>\n<p>Di fase ini AI membantu menggali:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>siapa saja pemain yang sudah melayani problem domain ini,</li>\n<li>apa pendekatan mereka,</li>\n<li>dimana celah kompetitif yang nyata,</li>\n<li>apa ekspektasi user yang spesifik.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Analogi yang bagus: jika ide Anda adalah hipotesis, market research adalah uji pertama terhadap realitas pasar. Ia memastikan Anda tidak sedang membangun jawaban untuk pertanyaan yang salah.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kenapa-ini-penting\">Kenapa ini penting?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kenapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Banyak ide AI-native terus bergerak ke coding karena mereka terasa \"menarik\" saja. Market research membatasi kelincahan ini. Ia menuntut bahwa fokus problem bukan sekadar menarik secara internal, tetapi relevan secara eksternal.</p>\n<p>Tanpa fase ini, planning bisa tetap tajam secara teknis, tetapi tidak terikat ke demand pasar. BMAD ingin menghindari product-led tunnel vision.</p>\n<h2 id=\"output-yang-berguna\">Output yang berguna<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#output-yang-berguna\"></a></h2>\n<p>Setelah research, Anda seharusnya memiliki:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>pemahaman kompetitor yang kontekstual,</li>\n<li>sinyal peluang yang nyata,</li>\n<li>poin diferensiasi awal,</li>\n<li>risiko pasar yang sebaiknya diwaspadai.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Itu membuat planning tidak lagi dimulai dari intuisi semata, tetapi dari realitas eksternal yang lebih stabil.</p>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171633\">BMAD brainstorming memperjelas ide sebelum requirement</a> — BMAD brainstorming memperjelas ide sebelum requirement</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a> — BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">analysis-phase (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">market-research (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-native (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171633\">BMAD brainstorming memperjelas ide sebelum requirement</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171635\">BMAD domain research memaksa pemahaman logika industri sebelum solusi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171825\">Simulasi BMAD analysis phase: invoice app untuk freelancer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{